When submitting bug reports, please:

 * Provide a description of what you were trying to do, and what happened instead
 * Indicate the functions that are misbehaving
 * Specify whether you were using the functions in a worksheet or in VBA code

For worksheet function misbehavior, please copy in the formula you were trying to use,
or attach a minimal Excel sheet that demonstrates the problem.

For VBA code, if possible please copy in the misbehaving piece of your source and
indicate the number and description of any run-time error that's thrown.

